LayerName: To provide you with the most accurate and personalized virtual try-on experience, our solution creates a realistic 3D avatar based on your body profile. This avatar helps simulate how clothing will look and fit on your unique physique. To achieve this, we use a combination of manual input and advanced machine learning techniques based on the following personal data: 1. Age Range Your age range helps us estimate typical body composition associated with your life stage. This ensures your avatar reflects realistic proportions and characteristics. 2. Height Establishes the overall scale of your avatar and provides proportional accuracy across limbs and torso. 3. Weight Used alongside height to determine overall body mass and shape, which impacts clothing fit and avatar realism. 4. Body Shape Helps us model the overall silhouette and balance of your avatar’s torso, hips, and shoulders. 5. Fitness Level Provides insight into muscle tone, body composition, contributing to a more lifelike and personalized avatar. 6. Main Measurements (Chest, Waist, Hips) Key for defining torso proportions and ensuring a precise digital fit. 7. Body Photos Front and side photos of your body are used by our machine learning models to extract precise body measurements. This enables us to automatically and accurately replicate your real-world shape in 3D. 8. Face Photos Front and side photos of your face allows us to generate a realistic facial likeness for your avatar. This step is optional but enhances the personalization of your digital twin. Why We Collect This Information All of this data is used solely to create a more precise and realistic digital twin avatar. This allows the app to: Create a highly accurate 3D avatar tailored to your actual body Simulate garment fit, size, and style with precision Improve clothing recommendations based on your true measurements Offer a realistic and confidence-boosting try-on experience Your Privacy Matters We take your privacy seriously. All personal data is: Consent-based: All data is collected only with your clear permission. Secure storage: Photos and personal data are encrypted and stored securely, deleted right after creating your 3D model. Strict usage: Your data is used exclusively for avatar creation and virtual try-on. No sharing: We never share your data or images with third parties without your explicit consent.
